F%2Flucashubbard.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2Fjam-session-video-player.png&a=w%3D256%26h%3D181%26fm%3Dpng%26q%3D90&cd=2022-03-11T15%3A19%3A47 256w,/_gatsby/image/50b7a908ae26e9751337340b4f2787f5/4cd2ed5d4e1ad800fbf26b67dc60cb8a/jam-session-video-player.png?u=https%3A%2F%2Flucashubbard.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2Fjam-session-video-player.png&a=w%3D512%26h%3D362%26fm%3Dpng%26q%3D90&cd=2022-03-11T15%3A19%3A47 512w,/_gatsby/image/50b7a908ae26e9751337340b4f2787f5/7b7d70bb71fe6cc57e3e3f0ef7239896/jam-session-video-player.png?u=https%3A%2F%2Flucashubbard.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2Fjam-session-video-player.png&a=w%3D1024%26h%3D725%26fm%3Dpng%26q%3D90&cd=2022-03-11T15%3A19%3A47 1024w\",\"sizes\":\"(min-width: 1024px) 1024px, 100vw\"}},\"layout\":\"constrained\",\"width\":1024,\"height\":725},\"alt\":\"\",\"className\":\"wp-image-2805 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\",\"data-wp-inline-image\":\"3\"}</script><figcaption>Jam Session player</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Future Updates</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In time, there are a few changes I would like to make to my website. I would like to create a gallery component to display my photos. It would allow me to organize photos into separate albums and display the selected album in an attractive grid similar to the Jam Session player described above. The projects on the web development portfolio page are pulled from markdown files for easy updates. I would like to add something similar to the video portfolio page. Finally, my design shows blog post filtering based on tags. Once implemented, users will be able to click on the tag buttons at the top of the blog listing to filter the posts being displayed.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"id":"cG9zdDoyNzg0","slug":"building-my-portfolio-site-and-blog","__params":{"slug":"building-my-portfolio-site-and-blog"}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3159585216"]}